metadata.name: Aave White Mile High T-Shirt
metadata.description:
This item was present at ETHDenver 2023 as either a giveaway or sold merchandise. This NFT represents a unique way to utilize tokenized merchandise for future events/drops. Check out this link for more info on this company: https://aave.com

This NFT is secured through on-chain storage fees. NFTs with delinquent storage balances cannot be transferred and the 4K Protocol uses the NFT itself as collateral if storage fees are not paid. You can view and top-up this item's storage fee balance at https://vault.4k.com/collectible/ethereum/0x50648D7d3eAD1D899fa53fD7001060Bb14592028/1.

Any NFT issued by 4K is redeemable for its physical counterpart anytime. To redeem, go to https://vault.4k.com/collectible/ethereum/0x50648D7d3eAD1D899fa53fD7001060Bb14592028/1. If you have any questions, you can reach us at help@4k.com.
